metadata.name: Dance post mortem
metadata.description:
After dying with the sweet poison of passion and love, you learn that the darkest voices of your hell will always be with you, putting on masks that will protect you from much suffering...
The gloom of your soul will become a beautiful black dress which you will wear with lust when dancing with your demons.
Welcome to the dance of darkness and elegance, welcome to the part of you that you have always escaped.
